#originalTopic=Healthcare_Should_Be_Available_For_Everyone
 Health care. I am in a private health care scheme through my employer. And I jumped at it. The NHS produces doctors who will see you quicker if you are registered to BUPA. The same doctors.  /> I once saw doctors as the last hope of idealism. Realism won that one again.  /> 